  <brief_title>Reverse Shoulder Arthroplasty With or Without Concomitant Latissimus and Teres Major Transfer for Shoulder Pseudoparalysis With Teres Minor Dysfunction</brief_title>
  <official_title>Reverse Shoulder Arthroplasty With or Without Concomitant Latissimus and Teres Major Transfer for Shoulder Pseudoparalysis With Teres Minor Dysfunction: A Prospective, Randomized Investigation</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
